  <h2>How much mulch do I need?</h2>
  <p>Mulch volume is calculated from area and depth. A 2-inch layer is common for refreshing existing beds, while 3 inches may be better for new beds or stronger weed suppression.</p>
  <h2>Bagged mulch vs bulk mulch</h2>
  <p>Bagged mulch is convenient for small jobs. Bulk mulch is usually easier and more economical once your project reaches several cubic yards.</p>
